We recommended that the Management:

Ensure that the MPDC closely coordinate with the Local Chief Executive and other members of the Municipal Planning and Development Council for the implementation of priority projects under the Municipality’s Local Development Plan to see to it that these plans are carried out on a timely manner and its purpose be achieved for the benefit of its constituents;

